Title: Book Review - Superminds by Thomas Malone
Slug: supermind
Date: 2019-05-18 8:00
Category: Blog 
Tags: AI,book,review,library,markets
Author: wykeith
Summary: The author explains the concepts of superminds operating in society as a consequence of collective intelligence. He defines collective intelligence as the result of groups of individuals acting together in ways that seem intelligent or purposeful. This book teaches us how to recognise the characteristics of superminds and tap on their superpowers.